Package: rprojroot
Title: Finding Files in Project Subdirectories
Version: 1.3.2.9000
Authors@R: person("Kirill", "M\u00fcller", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "krlmlr+r@mailbox.org", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1416-3412"))
Description: Robust, reliable and flexible paths to files below a
    project root. The 'root' of a project is defined as a directory
    that matches a certain criterion, e.g., it contains a certain
    regular file.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.0)
Imports:
    backports
Suggests:
    testthat,
    mockr,
    knitr,
    withr,
    rmarkdown
